    ðŸ”¹ `gcc file1.o file2.o -o program` --> ðŸ”— Link object files (`file1.o` and `file2.o`) into an executable program named `program`.
    ðŸ”¹ `gcc -I/path/to/include/directory file.c` --> ðŸ“ Add a directory to search for header files.
    ðŸ”¹ `gcc -L/path/to/lib/directory -lmath` --> ðŸ“š Add a directory to search for libraries and link the `math` library to the program.

